    java.io.Serializable

    public class PatientBean
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    A bean for storing data about a patient. A bean's purpose is to store data. Period. Little or no functionality is to be added to a bean (with the exception of minor formatting such as concatenating phone numbers together). A bean must only have Getters and Setters (Eclipse Hint: Use Source > Generate Getters and Setters? to create these easily)
